    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Using homebrew on OSX in Enterprise Environments]]></title>
    <link href="http://www.macops.io/homebrew/OSX/Enterprise/MacPorts/curl/2013/05/31/using-homebrew-in-enterprise-environments/"/>
